      • updateAllSpeciesList

        public static void updateAllSpeciesList()
        Updates the all species tracking list by getting all the invasive species. Gets a trackings species if it exists, if not creates one. The checks the all species arraylist for the species. If it does not exist in there already, puts it in. The end result is a allSpecies arraylist that contains all the tracking species.
